rmk: Morning. Primary forest in unburned part. Pair in the canopy.

This was taken by the roadside where a pair(a male and female) was seen at an adjacent forested region. Only one of them was seen flying out from the trees while the other one kept calling. In fact, this pair has been living in the area for quite some time(I've seen them multiple times, though this is the only time I managed to record their sounds). This place was at a public place hence some degree of anthropogenic noises(such as car sounds), and I've edited the recording using Audacity to cut off some unusually loud human noises.
